org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT spree_option_values.*, spree_option_types.position AS option_type_position FROM spree_option_values INNER JOIN spree_option_types ON spree_option_types.id = spree_option_values.option_type_id INNER JOIN spree_option_value_variants ON spree_option_value_variants.option_value_id = spree_option_values.id INNER JOIN spree_variants ON spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_variants.id = spree_option_value_variants.variant_id WHERE spree_option_types.filterable = "$1" AND spree_variants.product_id IN ("$2", "$3", "$4") ORDER BY option_type_position, spree_option_values.position
